data.description: 29.70 acres which backs to open space this is such an amazing opportunity to finish this home and walk into sweat equity, the home is in the final stages of construction and will need to be completed. Estimate to complete the remaining items is about $85,000 Oversized garage with insulated door a car lovers dream measures a super large 23 x 35! Home is about 85% complete most if not all of the materials are on the property. Basement is unfinished but roughed in for plumbing, ceilings are 10 ft All the exterior doors are 8 ft doors. Ceiling height in the great room is 28 ft at the peak. Radiant heat, walk in pantry, his/hers closets (hers closet could be nursery or an incredible closet). Water closet in master roughed in for bidet & toilet; 32 sq ft digital steam shower roughed in with bench. Cabinets close birch 42" All the matching crown molding/toe kicks/trim are on site. Appliances are black stainless steel, smart fridge, smart double ovens, gas range. Dog wash & showers are marble. Natural black slate floors & natural hand scraped acacia floors. Tub on the main floor is a jetted tub. Interior doors are on site but not installed; all solid doors for bathrooms, bedrooms & for the closets. Electrical panel is upgraded to a double panel. 5,000 gallon propane tank, leased on site. Windows Anlin windows Hardie/stone siding, Juliette balcony. Will need to reapply for Building and Septic permits are expired and well will require completion buyer & agent to verify with county all rules and allowances. Amazing opportunity, subdivide (must verify with county) and still have plenty of space for the home. REDUCED MOTIVATED SELLER BRING OFFERS!THIS IS AN INCREDIBLE OPPORTUNITY TO WALK INTO SOME SWEAT EQUITY. GREAT CHANCE TO CUSTOMIZE TO SUIT YOUR NEEDS! Please see supplements for additional documents. Sellers will work with Buyers to transfer all plans & permits available upon request.
